{"tid":149554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翁靜晶：冇咗有線新聞部係最大嘅損失","createTime":"2017-03-09T11:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T15:59:10.000Z","uid":20933,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3432f81cfda3151c663235c1199f2eb03608b11","tid":149554,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489055849_bd55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489055849_bd55.jpg&h=c1cb0a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然翁靜晶喺13年試過cut唔到有線，更揚言：「大不了就法庭見！」(新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1sh0VNk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1sh0VNk&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3cc2fd3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1sh0VNk</a> )不過，佢對於有線告急都覺得有啲感慨。<br />\n<br />\n翁靜晶接受《蘋果》訪問時講到：「我見到呢個消息(有線告急)覺得有啲唏噓，畢竟呢個電視台都陪咗我哋咁多年，我以前都幫佢主持過一啲節目；再加埋佢哋嘅新聞真係做得好好㗎，呢幾日有一宗假結婚嘅偵查報道做得真係好出色，個個都讚，我覺得個新聞部最值得惋惜嘅損失。」"},{"pid":"96d9c69db068e8833cbe984acced55d34e6421f5","tid":149554,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:13:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170309&amp;guid=56406028&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170309%26guid%3D56406028%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=dea7210d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170309%26guid%3D56406028%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=9e12e1b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170309&amp;guid=56406028&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"9e4a33182ce2ca0f93f8770932971deb5db08fb5"